<F P=106> [Article by A. V. Konstantinova, Ye. F. Pen, A. M. Sinyukov, </F>
V. V. Shelkovnikov; UDC 535.417:773.93] 
  [Abstract] Results are described in this article of studies 
dealing with the optical amplification in amorphous photopolymer 
materials GFPM-633 which exhibit a high sensitivity in the red 
spectral region. The material is designed for recording phase 
holograms by the He-Ne laser radiation (_l_=632.8 nm). The 
